5. ## MockHttpMessageHandler Helper
6. 
7. Reusable mock for tools that use `HttpClient`:
8. 
9. ```csharp
10. public class MockHttpMessageHandler : HttpMessageHandler
11. {
12.     private readonly string _response;
13.     private readonly HttpStatusCode _statusCode;
14. 
15.     public MockHttpMessageHandler(
16.         string response = "",
17.         HttpStatusCode statusCode = HttpStatusCode.OK)
18.     {
19.         _response = response;
20.         _statusCode = statusCode;
21.     }
22. 
23.     protected override Task<HttpResponseMessage> SendAsync(
24.         HttpRequestMessage request,
25.         CancellationToken cancellationToken) =>
26.         Task.FromResult(new HttpResponseMessage
27.         {
28.             StatusCode = _statusCode,
29.             Content = new StringContent(_response)
30.         });
31. }
32. ```
